      "text": "for years and years"
    },
    {
      "start": 276.56,
      "end": 278.52,
      "text": "and she did other jobs"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.52,
      "end": 280.02,
      "text": "like she was in a shed"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.02,
      "end": 280.68,
      "text": "she was a chef"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.68,
      "end": 282.3,
      "text": "she worked here and there"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.3,
      "end": 284.28,
      "text": "and she was trying to find herself"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.28,
      "end": 286.14,
      "text": "because she felt like"
