      "text": "to find her own true passion"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.74,
      "end": 290.72,
      "text": "she was just paying the family bills"
    },
    {
      "start": 290.72,
      "end": 293.32,
      "text": "so finally, recently"
    },
    {
      "start": 293.32,
      "end": 295.0,
      "text": "she came back to acting"
    },
    {
      "start": 295.0,
      "end": 296.66,
      "text": "and we got to see her"
